生意。晒叫野食！<br />\n聽到條女同其中一隻厹叫左兩碗10小辣，屌佢老味，笑撚到我丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食10小辣就不如叫清湯算啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係笑而不語，大大聲落左位2小辣。見到對面果兩件垃圾即刻柒頭dum低晒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點先其餘厹見勢色不對，竟然叫撚左兩碗中辣一碗大辣！屌佢老味咩意思先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家食下野姐，食得太辣根本傷身，你叫乜撚野中辣大辣呀死厹！一陣屎忽開撚晒花好得意呀！咁上位嘅咩屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總結：食譚叫中辣大辣嘅都係厹契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d894ddafcadf26083fb641e3db0de693dd54c1f3","tid":258381,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我正式宣傳！食譚叫中辣以上嘅都係外來腥港人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e948e4103a6cbb97c57f56a7bbabf29244909bbd","tid":258381,"uid":50323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"廢到"},{"pid":"215975aa76c5eded3835250b05d6620d25d7dc91","tid":258381,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n唔叫雙特辣不如食清湯"},{"pid":"72ac230687808b4ec4b30ed7ab949299f5114dbb","tid":258381,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"唔明啲厹契弟咁鍾意爆菊就去搵基佬搞基啦，扮咩野食得辣呀死厹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c836610793cbae6b51e7e0a76c538e89a4e88b0","tid":258381,"uid":101693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"食開中辣-大辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：可以食特辣，不過傷身就不了"},{"pid":"71d2ce8cbb81830a4470d38eee7cdf6c1c95bf98","tid":258381,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,